10... Qxd6 11. h3
{ White often plays this because they're scared of the pin with ...Bg4. } 11...
Qg3
{ This move doesn't win, but it does make your opponent spill their coffee. We are threatening ...Bxh3. Of course, the queen can't be taken because of the pin. }
12. Ng5 { 12.Kh1  Bxf2  is just a free pawn. } 12... h6 13. Qf3 Qxf3 14. Nxf3
Nb4
