{ Supporting the knight and preparing to develop the bishop. This gives White the option to give us an unusual pawn structure with doubled d-pawns if they choose to trade knights.   4...Nxc3  5.dxc3  is possible but risky. White can use the open lines in the center to develop very rapidly. }
