{ Sticking with our strategy of putting White under as much pressure as possible.  5...e6  is also possible, transposing to a variation of the French that is considered fine for Black. }
6. Qxd4 { 6.Nxd4  Nxe5  allows Black to grab a central pawn. } 6... e6
